## Animation & Interactions

### Animation Principles

**Duration:**
```
Micro (hover): 150ms
Standard: 250ms
Complex: 400ms
Page transitions: 300ms
```

**Easing:**
```
Default: ease-in-out
Entering: ease-out (starts fast, decelerates)
Exiting: ease-in (starts slow, accelerates)
Bouncy (sparingly): cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55)
```

### Hover States

**Links:**
```
Default: Primary color
